The paper discusses the transmission of short packets in wireless systems, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The paper also mentions the need for ultra-high reliability and low latency, which are topics related to control systems (cs.SY) and multimedia (cs.MM). Additionally, the paper discusses the suboptimal methods used to transmit metadata in current systems, which is a topic related to cryptography and security (cs.CR).
